description: Inspired by the unwavering spirit of the Filipino street dog, Azkal (AZK) rises above the chaos of the crypto world. This meme token embodies resilience and determination, offering a unique presence in a market of fleeting trends.

This meme token pays tribute to the legendary Manny Pacquiao, embodying his strength, resilience, and iconic Filipino pride. With a bold design inspired by the "Pacman" himself, it combines cultural heritage and innovation, making it a standout in the world of cryptocurrency.
